⸻

compatibility

beast language is a subset and restructuring of normal english

normal english can still be used
beast language just makes structure visible

⸻

core axiom cluster

#axiom small error = full error
#axiom good intent matters but action decides outcome
#axiom map, do not replace
#axiom lock the core, let the edges explore
#axiom go wild, but only keep what survives

⸻

closing

beast language v1 is not meant to be perfect

it is meant to be:
	•	usable
	•	stable
	•	compressible
	•	expandable

goal

turn chaos into clean artifacts without destroying meaning



